Quick installation
==================

1) Run "autoreconf -i", if you got the source from git.
2) Run "./configure".
3) Run "make".
4) Run "make install" as root.
5) Create a global configuration file /etc/mjsrc or a private ~/.mjsrc.
   For example:
     "cat doc/example/mjsrc doc/example/mjsrc-colors-green > ~/.mjsrc"
6) Enjoy!
